            "value": "Currently noController setting in viewRenderer reset for each controller.\nI think noController setting should be global for all controller.\n\nin my bootstrap:\n\n$c=Zend_Controller_Front::getInstance();\n$vr=Zend_Controller_Action_HelperBroker::getExistingHelper(\"viewRenderer\");\n$vr->setViewSuffix( \"php\"); \/\/ globally setting\n$vr->setNoController( true );\n\n"
