                        "name": "superbiji",
                        "displayName": "Superbiji",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "my path layout:\n\napp\/\n     controllers\/\n     views\/\n     views\/scripts\n     views\/scripts\/form1.php\n     views\/scripts\/form2.php\n     views\/scripts\/header.php -> global\n     views\/scripts\/footer.php -> global\n\nI don't like to assign header and footer to view vars,\nI love the simple PHP way (using include) ^^\n\nin my form1.php:\n\ninclude \"header.php\"\n\n\/\/ ....\n\ninclude \"footer.php\"\n\n\nthat's why i want to use noController option in viewRenderer\n",
