                        "name": "matthew",
                        "displayName": "Matthew Weier O'Phinney",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "I've added a 'neverController' flag to the ViewRenderer to allow the option of globally disabling the controller subdirectory for resolving view script paths. Usage is:\n\n{code}\n$viewRenderer->setNeverController(true);\n{code}\n\nAs of r5306.",
